      için pedagojik bir formata dönüştürülmüştür.
      This educational material is inspired by Daniel Bourke's "Zero to Mastery
      Learn PyTorch for Deep Learning". Content has been translated into Turkish,
      restructured, and adapted into a pedagogical format for educational technologists.

